        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "In the midst of these appalling horrors, time, it seems, has hastened still more in its bewildered flight, and already we have reached the anniversary of that foul deed, the blackest that has ever defiled the history of the human race.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "This crime was committed after long, hypocritical premeditation, and no pang of remorse, no vestige of shame, caused those myriads of accomplices to stay their hands.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "There were certain dastardly deeds, certain acts of profanation, certain lies, at which those hordes that came to us from Asia hesitated; an instinctive reverence still restrained them; and, moreover, in those times they did not destroy with such impudent cynicism, invoking the God of Christians in a burlesque pathos of prayer!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "King Albert of Belgium, dispossessed to day of his all and banished to a hamlet-what tribute of admiration and homage can we offer him worthy of his acceptance and sufficiently enduring?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "Upon tablets of flawless marble let us carve his name in deep letters so that it may be well insured against the fugitiveness of our French memories, which, alas! have sometimes proved a little untrustworthy, at least in face of the age long infamies of Germany.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "As for Queen Elizabeth, let each one of us dedicate to her a shrine in his soul.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "One of the most dreaded duties that falls almost invariably to the lot of queens is having to reign over adopted countries while exiled from their own.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "In the special case of this young martyred queen, this doom of exile which has befallen her, and many other queens, must be a far more exquisite torture, added to all the other evils endured, for a crushing fatality has come and separated her for ever from all who were once her own people, even from that noble woman, all devotion and charity, who was her mother.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "And she is by the side of the poor who have lost their all by pillage or fire; by the side of the wounded who are suffering or dying; to them, too, she is a companion, comforting the lowliest with her adorable simplicity, shedding on all the increasing bounty of her exquisite compassion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59234_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59234/6037_59234_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "Oh, may she be blest, reverenced, and glorified!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "ALL SOULS' DAY WITH THE ARMIES AT THE FRONT",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "Each grave is decked with at least four fine tricolours, their flagstaffs planted in the ground, two at the head, two at the foot, and an infinite number of flowers and wreaths tied with ribbons.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "There are fifteen of these graves, each with its four flags, making sixty flags in all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "And in the bitter autumn wind they flutter almost gaily, unceasingly, all these strips of bunting, they wanton in the air, intermingle, and their bright colours shine out more conspicuously.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "During these days of festival, the rest of the cemetery is also very full of flowers, but it looks dull and colourless compared with that corner sacred to our soldiers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "It was very gloomy in that cemetery, under an overcast sky, whence fell a semi darkness already wintry in aspect.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "All the little churches-those at least that the barbarians have not destroyed-had been decorated that day with all that the villages could muster in the way of flags, banners, tapers and wreaths.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "And they were too small, these churches, to hold the crowds that flocked to them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "There were officers, soldiers, civil population, women mostly in mourning, whose eyes under their veils were reddened with secret tears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "Indeed what could better prepare them for the supreme sacrifice and for a death nobly met than these prayers, this music and even these flowers?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "They sang this morning, these improvised choristers, with a solemn transport.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "And again, as on the day of the funerals, all the little graves were blessed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "Oh let them take comfort!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6037_59239_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6037/59239/6037_59239_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6037",
        "content": "In spite of the simplicity of these little wooden crosses, almost all alike, nowhere are they cared for and honoured so well as at the front; in no other place could they receive such touching homage, such tribute of flowers, of prayers, of tears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    }
